2011_April 30 
First of all thanks to Christopher Nolan for gave a such a master
piece. this is the real master piece from Nolan. after memento such a
thrilling screenplay from the director. about the story, man who have
able to go to dreams and stealing their secrets also planting the some
other information which is assigned to him with his crew. Leo leads the
crew as Cobb.Ellen Page as Ariadne who is the best architecture in
their crew. From the Introduction to climax, visualization was perfect.
In the climax all are came to edge of their seat. Joseph Gordon , Tom
Hardy(Excellent performance), Ken Watanabe, Marion Cotillard(So cute,
all are done their work perfectly. and Finally Hats off to Christopher
Nolan.<br /><br />My Rating 10/10
